data.title: Careerwise Online
data.text:
Christopher Reid, B.A., DipEd, Ph.D. was born in Scotland, educated at the University of Oxford, LaSalle and Western Washington University.

His career has included teaching University, High School and Junior High School students as well as many successful years in business.

Chris regularly presents seminars to schools and to parent groups. He lives in Calgary, is married and has 2 children.

Chris is the founder and Executive Director of Careerwise Ltd.
